fields.description: Your concept model does not have to be pretty, but it must be full size and prove that your idea works. Use the image from Step 4: Ideation as a basis to build your concept model. Don't be afraid to find out that something in your ideation drawing doesn't work as you thought it would. This is why you make a concept model to prove that your idea is valid. Take pictures of your concept model and insert them below. The Concept model will be used as reference in Step 6: Engineering.
